c: 10
v: 5
t: "“Iye (Allah) ndiYemwe adapanga dzuwa kukhala lowala, ndi mwezi kukhala wounika; ndipo adaukonzera mbuto (masitesheni) kuti mudziwe kuchuluka kwa zaka ndi chiwerengero chake. Allah sadalenge zimenezo koma mwachoonadi (ndi cholinga cha nzeru). Akufotokoza Ayah (Zake) kwa anthu ozindikira"